    "Middeldorf began his study of art history in 1920-1921 initially under <a href=\"/wolfflinh\">Heinrich W\u00f6lfflin</a>, already retired, and <a href=\"/mayera\">August Liebmann Mayer</a>\u00a0at the University of Munich.": [
